  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days. Or message us on <a href="https://t.me/sunpebble">Telegram</a>.</p>

  <h2>Restore your purchase</h2>
  <p>Reinstalled or got a new phone? Open Dayroll → Settings → <em>Restore Purchase</em>.
     The unlock is tied to your Apple ID, so you'll never pay twice.</p>

  <h2>Where is my data?</h2>
  <p>On your device, and in your personal iCloud if sync is on. See the
     <a href="/dayroll/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
</Base>
